dcterms:description: The Development dataset consists of 46,496 scans of 6,236 eyes from 3,456 patients, collected from the Southampton Eye Unit. Eyes were scanned 7.7 times over 1.9 years on average at irregular time intervals.
dcterms:title: Development dataset

dcterms:description: The Unseen dataset is larger than the Development dataset, containing 114,062 scans of 7,253 eyes from 3,819 patients. Eyes were scanned 16.6 times over 3.5 years on average.
dcterms:title: Unseen dataset
